      <title>路易斯安那州禁止公共卫生工作者宣传新冠、流感和牛痘疫苗</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/12/20/nx-s1-5223440/louisiana-ban-public-health-promoting-covid-flu-mpox-vaccines-landry-rfk-jr-anti-vaccine</link>
